### **Slide 2 â€” Common Threats Targeting HR Teams**

| Threat Type                  | Description                                                | Example                                             |
| ---------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| **Phishing Resumes**         | Fake CVs containing malware attachments (.zip, .docm)      | â€œResume_John.docmâ€ installs a trojan.               |
| **Fake Job Portals**         | Imitation of Naukri/LinkedIn pages to steal HR credentials | HR logs into a clone portal.                        |
| **Social Engineering Calls** | Callers posing as candidates, vendors, or auditors         | â€œCan you confirm employee salary for verification?â€ |
| **Data Exfiltration**        | Insider copying candidate lists or payslips                | Disgruntled employee leaks data.                    |
| **Third-party Vendor Risks** | Weak security in external background agencies              | Data breach during verification.                    |

ğŸ§© Demo: Show a â€œfake job application emailâ€ and highlight red flags (mismatched domains, grammar, attachment types).

