### **Slide 5 â€” Social Engineering Defense for HR Teams**

Common Scenarios:
âš ï¸ â€œCandidateâ€ calls asking to confirm who handles recruitment for job openings.
âš ï¸ â€œVendorâ€ sends fake background verification requests.
âš ï¸ â€œAuditorâ€ requests employee data â€œurgentlyâ€.

ğŸ§© **Golden Rule:**

> â€œVerify first â€” share never.â€

âœ” Always verify caller identity via official contact list.
âœ” Donâ€™t share employee/candidate data over phone or SMS.
âœ” Report suspicious communications to IT/Security immediately.

ğŸ­ Activity: Role-play â€œimposter callerâ€ scenario and have HR identify red flags.

